OL,5,G1550 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt Manse on the Beach in Cloughey,
OL,7,     Fformer international rugby player
OL,8,     FBrian Robinson hosts. The guests
OL,9,     Flove the sea views, but two of
OL,10,     Fthem feel hot under the collar
OL,11,     Fafter a bad slumber.
OL,12,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FAt The Secret Garden Glamping in
OL,14,     FSkelmersdale, Lancashire, friends
OL,15,     FDerry and Mike host. The B&Bers
OL,16,     Fare ecstatic with their rooms, but
OL,17,     Ftwo guests feel a little hemmed in
OL,18,     Fby their hideaway.
