OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe final visit is to the
OL,7,     Fadults-only Hawthorn Hideaway in
OL,8,     FWalkeringham, run by Ronnie and
OL,9,     FJo. Derry and Mike are delighted
OL,10,     Fby the decor, while Shaun and
OL,11,     FHollie get a stunning surprise.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FOn the final day, the B&Bers meet
OL,14,     Fto discuss their feedback - from
OL,15,     Fdisappointing breakfasts, to
OL,16,     Fpulling off the covers on some
OL,17,     Fdodgy sleep scores - before the
OL,18,     Fwinner is announced.
