OL,6,     FAndy and Nicki Bruce try to build
OL,7,     Fan experimental flood-proof,
OL,8,     Ffloating house on an island in the
OL,9,     FRiver Thames. But building such a
OL,10,     Fcomplex design on a site with
OL,11,     Flimited access isn't easy.
